Feature: 5 Editing Feature Files in Azure DevOps
You have the possibility to **edit Feature Files directly in Azure DevOps**, if you use the Azure DevOps extension
and your Feature Files are stored in Azure DevOps repositories.
To do so, a button is placed on the top right (only in the extension) which takes you directly from the LivingDoc
to the source feature files.

Wihtin this editor, **Syntax highlighting** is also supported in Azure DevOps for the following languages:
- English
- German

